{"tid":1601574,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［國際戰線］戒嚴 = 核彈","createTime":"2019-09-29T05:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:21:44.000Z","uid":52200,"like":749,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":163,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5cb428ae4eb585bc7340a9d634cb1c0fe1c133","tid":1601574,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"各位，港共政權到依家都唔敢宣布戒嚴，係因為一宣布戒嚴，就意味著香港唔再係一個穩定嘅資本主義賭場，所有投行、基金都會即刻撤資。<br />\n<br />\n而到今日，香港已經實際上進入左戒嚴狀態。所有基本法賦與嘅人權，都可以因爲黑警唔順眼而被剝奪。<br />\n<br />\n行街shopping 俾人拉，出街帶口罩俾人打，搭巴士都會俾人查。香港已經唔再係自由城市。<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家今晚可以幫手係twitter 推呢個hashtag:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#MartialLawInHongKong</span></span><br />\n<br />\n推到走資潮出現！推到商家佬賴屎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要攬炒</span></span>"},{"pid":"feb4808a0ea99d9fd9ce366bbe3e9d77e94fab6c","tid":1601574,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:50:26.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"05abfc426ae3b69b40be3de925a4bd9e335d27ae","tid":1601574,"uid":50214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"新tag <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad103df94bf0a3dd4f21bd3d01bd10139232ba6","tid":1601574,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d060aa86456b3d20cc446e6c2ed71bc6c0311a6f","tid":1601574,"uid":52200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T05:51:39.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"d66b62cfca510dea3294f7f76941e3238dea16f8","tid":1601574,"uid":203619,