對中國抽'香港人權稅'，減輕自己負擔又發少啲國債！同時對香港抽較輕的税，支持香港經濟不被共產陣營吞拼<br />\n<br />\n'香港人權税'並沒有特定限制 ;每個國家各適其適 只要支持香港，容易執行就好<br />\n<br />\n香港人幫外國人食子彈，就是保護全球經濟增長、他們在香港的利益和 自由陣營的最前線 ，眼前的'新西柏林'意義重大，西方國家更沒理由， 無條件輸送金錢給中國請流氓打柒香港人 ，中國利用央企滋長邪惡，虐待香港人，全世界就有義務制裁它<br />\n<br />\n再冇其他選擇 香港人不講獨立不分化<br />\n一齊頂硬上！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"206dc802ab60acd65d3dafebecd3c043dfa84821","tid":1601574,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1228ab382cae1bac1f609661325004b6923a0dd","tid":1601574,"uid":91866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:11:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff8ad1cf333cb1d8ae807cfc93e6be6f1e60515e","tid":1601574,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4343f860e6e5c1a85947f16682bfc8ca147fed5b","tid":1601574,"uid":106331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:12:23.000Z","msg":"多謝港共提供核彈"},{"pid":"b640c9cef600f98a3dd9dbb897a7b7a2b94af317","tid":1601574,"uid":225488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:12:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"454e3e173e89a8a421a68dc36c6e3479bb1358c8","tid":1601574,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638f26cb41d8a86f9221729d2eddc9006e361cde","tid":1601574,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T06:13:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3d213d842f892c496212403281b472dc01f1d46","tid":1601574,"uid":270856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit